SUMMARY:Cherry Blossoms Waterfront 5K
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\n**Cherry Blossoms Are Peaking This Weekend! 🌸**\n**We’re throwing together an impromptu 5K for anyone who wants to catch the waterfront cherry blossoms in full bloom.**\n**The route is about 3.1 miles — give or take — along the PDX waterfront. We’ll start running at** **2:05 PM****\, take time for photos\, and wrap with group kudos.**\n\n**Join if you can — totally casual. Come for an easy cruise or go for that 5K PR.**\n\n**🌸🌸** **Families\, friends and all experience levels welcome!** **🌸🌸**\n\n**Meetup:** **We will meet at S Moody Ave and S Hall Street (street parking available in the area\, Parking Kitty app recommended)**\n\n**Route:** [AllTrails 5k map](https://www.alltrails.com/explore/custom-routes/waterfront-park-5k-5047cd5)
